T02D2621:120a-1: a'a rya mnydzu shr'i n'a ma sam g'i ti sarba mandala sto tra /
T02D2621:120a-3: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad la bstod pa /
T02D2621:120a-4: phyi dang nang dang de'i nang na //
T02D2621:120a-5: sku gsum bdag nyid la bzhugs pa //
T02D2621:120a-6: snying rje shes rab rjes zhugs pa //
T02D2621:120a-7: gzhon nu khyod la phyag 'tshal lo ;
T02D2621:120a-8: / rnam kun rnam par byang chub dang //
T02D2621:120a-9: rnam kun dri ma med pa dang //
T02D2621:120a-10: chos rnams kun la gnas pa dang //
T02D2621:120a-11: chos kun gcig tu ston pa dang //
T02D2621:120a-12: rnam kun tshul la 'jug pa dang //
T02D2621:120a-13: rnam kun tshul la gnas pa dang //
T02D2621:120a-14: rnam pa kun gyi don tshul gcig /'jam pa'i dbyangs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2621:120a-15: sgeg dang bzhad dang mi sdug dang //
T02D2621:120a-16: drag po'i ngo mtshar nyams bdag nyid //
T02D2621:120a-17: nyon mongs gcod dang shes rab can //
T02D2621:120a-18: dang po'i sangs rgyas khyod la 'dud //
T02D2621:120a-19: srid dang zhi ba spangs pa dang //
T02D2621:120a-20: srid dang zhi bar bzhugs par mdzad //
T02D2621:120b-0: zla ba gzhon @120b nu ltar mdzes pa //
T02D2621:120b-1: chos sku de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2621:120b-2: chos rnams thams cad stong nyid kyi //
T02D2621:120b-3: srog tu khyod ni bzhugs pa yin //
T02D2621:120b-4: mtshan ma la yang mtshan ma med //
T02D2621:120b-5: dbang phyug che la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2621:120b-6: khyod mi bzhugs na spros 'di la //
T02D2621:120b-7: ji ltar yang ni smon pa yin //
T02D2621:120b-8: khyed 'dir rjes su zhugs na ni //
T02D2621:120b-10: thog ma bar dang mthar dge ba //
T02D2621:120b-12: phrin las rjes su 'jug pa yin //
T02D2621:120b-13: sna tshogs ston la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2621:120b-14: lta ba rtog dag las 'tsho ba //
T02D2621:120b-15: rtsol dang dran dang ting 'dzin gyi //
T02D2621:120b-18: rang bzhin gyis ni kun rdzob dang //
T02D2621:120b-19: sems can rnams kyi bsdu ba dang //
T02D2621:120b-20: dge ba dri med snang ba dang //
T02D2621:120b-21: smin byed de la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2621:120b-22: zang zing mi 'jigs spyin byed dang //
T02D2621:120b-23: byams pa spyin byed mchog dang ni //
T02D2621:120b-24: chos spyin chos kyi dbang phyug gi //
T02D2621:120b-25: chen po de la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2621:120b-26: zhi gnas lhag mthong dag gi ni //
T02D2621:120b-27: shes rab pha rol phyin par 'gro //
T02D2621:120b-28: nyon mongs gcod pa'i shes rab kyi //
T02D2621:120b-29: ral gri bsnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2621:120b-30: sems can khams ni mgu ba dang //
T02D2621:120b-31: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa chen pos gnon //
T02D2621:120b-32: ba stan pa so so rang rig gi //
T02D2621:120b-33: skyob pa'i mgon la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2621:120b-34: go cha chen po bgos pa dang //
T02D2621:120b-35: 'jug pa che la gnas pa dang //
T02D2621:120b-36: so sor rtog par byed pa dang //
T02D2621:120b-37: bya ba nan tan de la bstod //
T02D2621:120b-38: spyin dang tshul khrims bzod brtson 'grus //
T02D2621:120b-39: bsam gtan shes rab stobs chen dang //
T02D2621:120b-40: thabs dang smon lam ye shes kyi //
T02D2621:120b-41: pha rol phyin la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2621:120b-42: brgya dang drug cu'i grangs kyis ni //
T02D2621:120b-43: dpal gyi byang chub 'gro ba'i gtso //
T02D2621:120b-44: gang zhig gcig kyang rnam bcu drug /'dod chags che la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2621:120b-45: byams pa'i ya lad bgos pa dang //
T02D2621:120b-46: shes srab go cha bgos pa dang //
T02D2621:120b-47: snying rje chen po blo ldan dang //
T02D2621:120b-48: ye shes tog la phag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2621:121a-2: 'jog cing skyob par byed pa dang //
T02D2621:121a-3: zab pa'i blo dang rgya mtsho bzhin //
T02D2621:121a-4: mi zad blo yi gter la 'dud //
T02D2621:121a-5: dbyer med spobs pa dag gis ni //
T02D2621:121a-6: stobs kyi pha rol phyin la 'dud //
T02D2621:121a-7: bgrod dka'i ngan song chen po las //
T02D2621:121a-9: mya ngan mun pa nges 'joms dang //
T02D2621:121a-11: rnam kun bdud rtsir 'dzag pa yi //
T02D2621:121a-13: 'od dpag med dang sprin med pa'i //
T02D2621:121a-14: nam mkha'i snying po phyag 'tshal bstod ;
T02D2621:121a-15: / sgrib pa thams cad sel ba la //
T02D2621:121a-17: dad dang brtson 'grus dran bsam gtan //
T02D2621:121a-18: shes rab kyis ni rjes bsrungs pa //
T02D2621:121a-19: srung ba med kyang 'od dag ni //
T02D2621:121a-20: gnon pa rmad byung rgyal la 'dud //
T02D2621:121a-21: chos kyi dbyings kyi bdag nyid kyi //
T02D2621:121a-22: la lar rdo rje sems dpa' dang //
T02D2621:121a-23: nyon mongs shes bya spangs pa yi //
T02D2621:121a-24: la lar rnam par snang mdzad dang //
T02D2621:121a-25: la lar rdo rje h'um mdzad dang //
T02D2621:121a-26: la lar padma gar dbang phyug / la lar rdo rje nyi ma ni //
T02D2621:121a-27: rgya chen rmad byung chen po mdzes //
T02D2621:121a-28: gcig gi bdag nyid rta mchog dang //
T02D2621:121a-29: la lar gsum gyi bdag nyid dang //
T02D2621:121a-30: gang zhig rnam lnga'i sna tshogs pa'i //
T02D2621:121a-31: skyob pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2621:121a-32: gnyis med 'byung ba'i chos nyid phyir //
T02D2621:121a-34: gcig kyang sna tshogs bdag nyid kyi //
T02D2621:121a-35: rnam par snang mdzad che la 'dud //
T02D2621:121a-36: mtshan brjod dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
T02D2621:121a-37: bstod pas bsod nams gang skyes pa //
T02D2621:121a-38: dge ba 'di yis sems can rnams //
T02D2621:121a-39: 'jam pa'i dbyangs ni 'grub par shog /'phags pa 'jam
T02D2621:121a-40: dpal gyi mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i dkyil 'khor
T02D2621:121a-42: slob dpon so ma shr'is mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02D2621:121a-44: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po ma h'a dzny'a na dang /
